content":"For example, a company has decided to deploy Windows 10 on all of their computers.","pos":[6264,6346]},{"content":"Each employee will keep the same computer, but the operating system on each computer will be updated.","pos":[6347,6448]},{"content":"An administrator runs the ScanState command-line tool on each computer, specifying the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>/hardlink<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> command-line option.","pos":[6454,6575]},{"content":"The ScanState tool saves the user state to a hard-link migration store on each computer, improving performance by reducing file duplication, except in certain specific instances.","pos":[6576,6754]},{"pos":[6760,7118],"content":"**Note**  \nAs a best practice, we recommend that you do not create your hard-link migration store until just before you perform the migration in order to migrate the latest versions of your files. You should not use your software applications on the computer after creating the migration store until you have finished migrating your files with Loadstate.","leadings":["","    "],"nodes":[{"content":"Note","pos":[2,6]},{"content":"As a best practice, we recommend that you do not create your hard-link migration store until just before you perform the migration in order to migrate the latest versions of your files. You should not use your software applications on the computer after creating the migration store until you have finished migrating your files with Loadstate.","pos":[11,354],"nodes":[{"content":"As a best practice, we recommend that you do not create your hard-link migration store until just before you perform the migration in order to migrate the latest versions of your files.","pos":[0,185]},{"content":"You should not use your software applications on the computer after creating the migration store until you have finished migrating your files with Loadstate.","pos":[186,343]}]}]},{"content":"On each computer, an administrator installs the company's standard operating environment (SOE), w